      "id": "definite_adj_predicate",
      "levels": [{"front": "the happy man (noun phrase) vs. The man is happy. (sentence)", "back": "الرجل السعيد — الرجل سعيد.", "romanized": "ar-rajul as-sa'id — ar-rajul sa'id.", "grammarNote": "Key distinction: الرجل السعيد (the happy man) = both definite, modifier. الرجل سعيد (The man is happy) = predicate adjective stays INDEFINITE. This definiteness difference is how you tell noun phrases from equational sentences."}]
